Team collaboration features
Technical Implementation:
Backend: Django REST Framework
Database: PostgreSQL (complex queries, relationships)
Caching: Redis for frequently accessed projects
Async Tasks: Celery for email notifications
Real-time: Django Channels for WebSockets
Testing: pytest with 80%+ coverage
Documentation: Swagger/OpenAPI
Advanced Features:
Rate limiting on API endpoints
Full-text search for tasks
API versioning
Filtering by status, user, deadline
Task dependencies
Activity timeline
Deployment:
Dockerize with docker-compose
Deploy to AWS EC2 or Railway
CI/CD with GitHub Actions
Environment configuration
Monitoring and logging
